ygData.messageBody:
Nah, I dun want a server switch anymore, but I dun mind play in other
server under part-time basis (which, it's kinda waste of time, so meaning I
wont play more than 5% in other servers, hehe).

[SMTP:sccheng@...] wrote:
> hey guys,
> i was playing abit last nite when suddenly a message bout a new server
coming up... just yesterday... anyone plan on shifting? hehe... i have
already researved those fav names i like on that server liaoz... hehe...
>
> if the whole guild is shifting... i dont mind doing it once... but no
more than once... also another good way of avoiding QHD...
>
> btw... y Enteri say no support? u just want guild war isit? then i think
the VZ or TZ will be a better place to be... since u cant really have

> cheers,
